{"tid":1241872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[建制派mon post入] 坦白講 你地做好準備下次選舉配票實比民建聯過橋抽板","createTime":"2019-06-19T00:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T02:20:13.000Z","uid":171273,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bfc1d2bc8caf86326a21fc2eed882f613ad9ae8d","tid":1241872,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:52:43.000Z","msg":"下半年就區議會選舉<br />\n<br />\n而家送中單野 民怨沸騰 <br />\n<br />\n上年建制加泛民都係得140萬票<br />\n<br />\n而家條街走左200萬人出黎<br />\n<br />\n亦都大把黃絲廢青會做首投族<br />\n<br />\n區議會會輸幾多席自己諗<br />\n<br />\n你地有黨科水比資源都無機會派糉搞蛇宴<br />\n<br />\n立法會仲有無咁多鐵票？ <br />\n<br />\n比例代表制 你地識配票優勢好大<br />\n<br />\n泛民呢方面無你地咁精準<br />\n<br />\n但泛民支持者人數而家多你幾多 你自己計下配票比起以前難幾多<br />\n<br />\n無區議會 立法會更難選<br />\n<br />\n到時立法會配票 你地班所謂隊友 <br />\n<br />\n尤其建制派之首既民建聯 錢既利益重要 定黨性重要<br />\n<br />\n我諗大家心入面最明白<br />\n<br />\n尤其係你 工聯會麥美娟 <br />\n<br />\n喧賓奪主 民建聯都未出聲 你就開聲<br />\n<br />\n我等睇各位建制派 後知後覺比自己人出賣<br />\n<br />\n真係諗起都興奮<br />\n<br />\n好自為之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee9429c25184d19b0f8b922d4c9817cd9359a0a","tid":1241872,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:54:59.000Z","msg":"慢慢爭取功能組別掌心雷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c84a03b34b017e3a8d1083bac658ec8dc7bc68","tid":1241872,"uid":171273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:57:32.000Z","msg":"見到工聯會成世二奶命比民建聯騎撚住<br />\n<br />\n而家仲要搞壇咁既野 等比經民聯/新民黨取代啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ed1b566fe67003f12e98540a1e35b20f18681a","tid":1241872,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:58:35.000Z","msg":"周恩來文革串左毛澤東一句造子孫孽<br />\n<br />\n比人清算到臨死 自己好好參透下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36962dbfefda6511a4a1bc69d69c8163f4fcaf50","tid":1241872,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350b5b27ace23db60f067f8aafc871c5b1c9f370","tid":1241872,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:01:36.000Z","msg":"麥美娟<br />\n<br />\n你地點出黎選?<br />\n<br />\n你唔好諗住選喇<br />\n<br />\n民建聯配票益葉劉都唔會益你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話哂林鄭失勢 票又唔多<br />\n<br />\nD票分比葉劉新民黨做造皇者 定係捧你工聯會呢D周融之流<br />\n<br />\n自己估下你大佬會點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1691164cefa06b9f4098604b546eb2d9c1f4e47","tid":1241872,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614f07cbb5559dae91126bebb261f162ef8cfab3","tid":1241872,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:07:48.000Z","msg":"我擺明分化你班建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過你自己諗下連林鄭都不能服眾既時侯 下面班友仲會唔會配票配得咁公平囉<br 